%body
  %header
    = render "header"

  .main
    %section.main__topDl
      .main__topDl__title 人生を変えるフリマアプリ
      .main__topDl__present
        FURIMAはだれでもかんたんに出品・購入できる
        %br
        フリマアプリです
      .main__topDl__banner
        .main__topDl__banner__link
          =link_to "#" do
            =image_tag("badge/app-store.svg", alt:"App-Store_Banner", class: "main__topDl__banner__link__badge")
        .main__topDl__banner__link
          =link_to "#" do
            =image_tag("badge/google-play.svg", alt:"Google-Play_Banne", class: "main__topDl__banner__link__badge")

    %section.main__reason
      .main__reason__title
        %h2.main__reason__title__text FURIMAが選ばれる3つの理由
        .main__reason__title__bar
      %ul.main__reason__lists
        %li.main__reason__lists__list
          =image_tag("pict/pict-reason-01.jpg", alt:"Exhibition-image", class: "main__reason__lists__list__img")
          .main__reason__lists__list__number 1
          .main__reason__lists__list__subTitle
            %span.main__reason__lists__list__subTitle--mainColor 3分
            ですぐに出品
          .main__reason__lists__list__description スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる！
        %li.main__reason__lists__list-center
          =image_tag("pict/pict-reason-02.jpg", alt:"Easy-image", class: "main__reason__lists__list__img")
          .main__reason__lists__list__number 2
          .main__reason__lists__list__subTitle
            %span.main__reason__lists__list__subTitle--mainColor シンプル
            で使いやすい
          .main__reason__lists__list__description めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ！
        %li.main__reason__lists__list
          =image_tag("pict/pict-reason-03.jpg", alt:"Free-image", class: "main__reason__lists__list__img")
          .main__reason__lists__list__number 3
          .main__reason__lists__list__subTitle
            手数料
            %span.main__reason__lists__list__subTitle--mainColor 業界最安
          .main__reason__lists__list__description 最大3%でお得に出品&amp;購入！

    %section.main__midDl
      .main__midDl__title 
        会員数日本一位
      .main__midDl__present
        FURIMAは、フリマアプリで最も人気。
        %br
        出品・購入回数も業界最多です！
        %br
        ほしかったあの商品に出会えるかもしれません
      .main__midDl__banner
        .main__midDl__banner__link
          =link_to "#" do
            =image_tag("badge/app-store.svg", alt:"App-Store_Banner", class: "main__midDl__banner__link__badge")
        .main__midDl__banner__link
          =link_to "#" do
            =image_tag("badge/google-play.svg", alt:"Google-Play_Banne", class: "main__midDl__banner__link__badge")

    %section.main__features
      .main__features__title
        %h2.main__features__title__text FURIMAの特徴
        .main__features__title__bar
      %ul.main__features__lists
        %li.main__features__lists__list
          =image_tag("icon/icon-01.png", alt:"Exhibition-image", class: "main__features__lists__list__img")
          .main__features__lists__list__subTitle 簡単に売り買いできる
          .main__features__lists__list__description スマホひとつで、いつでもどこでも簡単に出品・購入が可能！
        %li.main__features__lists__list
          =image_tag("icon/icon-03.png", alt:"Exhibition-image", class: "main__features__lists__list__img")
          .main__features__lists__list__subTitle 売上金は即日振込みに対応
          .main__features__lists__list__description 午前9時までに振込を依頼いただければ、翌日に指定の口座に入金いたします!
        %li.main__features__lists__list
          =image_tag("icon/icon-04.png", alt:"Exhibition-image", class: "main__features__lists__list__img")
          .main__features__lists__list__subTitle 様々な支払いに対応
          .main__features__lists__list__description お支払いは、クレジットカードだけでなく、ポイントや売上金など多彩な方法があります。

    %section.main__pickupCategory
      .main__pickupCategory__title ピックアップカテゴリー
      .main__pickupCategory__newItem
        =link_to "#" do
          新規投稿商品
      %ul.main__pickupCategory__itemLists
        - @new_items.each do |item|
          = render "itemList", {item: item}
    %section.main__pickupBrand
      .main__pickupBrand__title ピックアップブランド
      .main__pickupBrand__archive
        =link_to "#" do
          アーカイバ
      %ul.main__pickupBrand__itemLists
        - @rnd_items.each do |item|
          - unless item.buyer_id.presence
            = render "itemList_noView_soldItem", {item: item}
    %section.main__btmDl
      = render "btmDl"

  
  = render "footer"
    
  = render "exhibitionBtn"
  